      "summary": "DM-only — the true source of Thornhold's resonance crystal.",
      "images": [],
      "body": "\n# Deeproot Cavern (DM)\n\nBeneath [[Raven's Vale]] lies a network of crystalline tunnels. The lord-mayor\nof [[Thornhold]] has been quietly extracting resonance crystal here for two\ndecades. The deeper galleries are rumored to house something older.\n",
      "bodyHtml": "<h1>Deeproot Cavern (DM)</h1>\n<p>Beneath <a class=\"atlas-wikilink\" data-entity-id=\"ravens-vale\" href=\"#/entity/ravens-vale\">Raven's Vale</a> lies a network of crystalline tunnels. The lord-mayor\nof <a class=\"atlas-wikilink\" data-entity-id=\"thornhold\" href=\"#/entity/thornhold\">Thornhold</a> has been quietly extracting resonance crystal here for two\ndecades. The deeper galleries are rumored to house something older.</p>\n",
