      "images": [],
      "body": "\n# The Old Keep\n\nFew travelers have laid eyes on the keep and returned with a clear story.\nThose who have speak of [[A Lost King]] — though no record of such a ruler exists\nin the chronicles of [[Sunhaven]].\n",
      "bodyHtml": "<h1>The Old Keep</h1>\n<p>Few travelers have laid eyes on the keep and returned with a clear story.\nThose who have speak of <span class=\"atlas-broken-link\" title=\"Broken link: A Lost King\">A Lost King</span> — though no record of such a ruler exists\nin the chronicles of <a class=\"atlas-wikilink\" data-entity-id=\"sunhaven\" href=\"#/entity/sunhaven\">Sunhaven</a>.</p>\n",
