      "summary": "A red-stone mining city carved into the southern bluffs.",
      "images": [],
      "body": "\n# Thornhold\n\nThornhold is a fortified mining city perched above the [[Raven's Vale]].\nIt trades iron and rare resonance crystal with [[Sunhaven]] along the King's Road.\n\n## History\n\nFounded after the Sundering, Thornhold's walls were raised from the same red\nstone that gives the city its name. Travelers know it by its alias *The Red City*.\n\n## Notable places\n\n- The Iron Gate\n- Old Market\n- Foundry District\n",
      "bodyHtml": "<h1>Thornhold</h1>\n<p>Thornhold is a fortified mining city perched above the <a class=\"atlas-wikilink\" data-entity-id=\"ravens-vale\" href=\"#/entity/ravens-vale\">Raven's Vale</a>.\nIt trades iron and rare resonance crystal with <a class=\"atlas-wikilink\" data-entity-id=\"sunhaven\" href=\"#/entity/sunhaven\">Sunhaven</a> along the King&#39;s Road.</p>\n<h2>History</h2>\n<p>Founded after the Sundering, Thornhold&#39;s walls were raised from the same red\nstone that gives the city its name. Travelers know it by its alias <em>The Red City</em>.</p>\n<h2>Notable places</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>The Iron Gate</li>\n<li>Old Market</li>\n<li>Foundry District</li>\n</ul>\n",
      "frontmatter": {
